                <div class="tab-content">
                    <div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-script">
                        <div class="js-script-content-wrapper top-margin-script markdown-content">
                                                                                        <a href="https://github.com/knpuniversity/behat/edit/behat3/knpu/complex-delete.md" target="_blank" class="btn btn-default btn-circle pull-right js-tooltip" title="Edit on GitHub"><span class="fa fa-pencil"></span></a>
                                                                    <p>Time for a real challenge! Deleting products, it's actually a bit harder than you
might think. Here comes some curve balls -- eh eh like that baseball pun?</p>
<p>We need a delete button to remove individual products. BDD Time! Start with the
scenario:</p>
