<p>This is the first time we've seen <code>But</code>. But, it has the same functionality as <code>And</code>:
it extends a <code>Then</code>, <code>When</code> or <code>Given</code> and sounds natural. </p>
<p>Try it! Run just this scenario:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">./vendor/bin/behat features/product_admin.feature:42</div></code></pre>
