<p>Consider the row found!</p>
<h2 id="finding-links-and-buttons-in-a-row">Finding Links and Buttons in a Row <a class="headerlink" href="complex-delete#finding-links-and-buttons-in-a-row" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>To find the link, we don't want to use css: <code>$linkText</code> is the <em>name</em> of the text:
what a user would see on the site. Instead, use <code>$row-&gt;findLink()</code> and pass it
<code>$linkText</code>:</p>
