<p>To add the delete link, find <code>list.html.twig</code> and add a column called Actions. Since
you should POST to delete things, add a small form in each row, instead of a link
tag. Make the form point to the <code>product_delete</code> route and add <code>method="POST"</code>. And
instead of having fields, it only needs a submit button whose text is "Delete".
Add some CSS classes to make it look nice - don't get too lazy on me:</p>
