<p>For clarity, change <code>$link</code> to <code>$button</code> and <code>$linkText</code> to <code>$buttonText</code>.</p>
<p>This should solve all 99 of our problems. I even have enough confidence to remove
<code>@javascript</code> and the "break" line. Rerun the test!</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">./vendor/bin/behat features/product_admin.feature:42</div></code></pre>
<p>Finally green!</p>
